title: Ep. 986 - Twitter Will Be Woke Or Die Trying
description:
Twitter triggers a “poison pill” to stop Elon Musk’s hostile takeover, Trump endorses J.D. Vance in Ohio, and WH press secretary Jen Psaki refers to a reporter as a stupid S.O.B.

NBA star Jonathan Isaac has withstood immense pressure to conform to popular social issues. He’s now writing a book about his experience and is publishing with the Daily Wire. Pre-order your copy now: https://utm.io/ud96e. 

I’m exposing the most successful failure in government history. Stream Fauci Unmasked here: https://utm.io/ueogL.
